---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Taffy Town — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Taffy Town's Formic palletizer has handled 5.5 million pounds of taffy and counting — stacking 279,000+ cases and building nearly 4,300 pallets, with Full Service Automation and zero CapEx."
  ogTitle="Taffy Town — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="5.5M lbs automated · 279,000+ cases · nearly 4,300 pallets"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/taffy-town" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Taffy Town
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Taffy Town</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">From Hand-Stacking to 5.5 Million Pounds Automated & Counting: How Taffy Town Scaled with Formic</h1>
    <p class="lede">Taffy Town's Formic palletizer has handled 5.5 million pounds of taffy and counting — stacking 279,000+ cases, building nearly 4,300 pallets, and freeing a full-time role from the strain of hand-stacking.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/taffy-town-hero.jpg" alt="Taffy Town robotic palletizing cell" />
      <span class="dv-cap">Taffy Town · Utah</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Utah</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Family-owned candy maker</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Tradition</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">A century of taffy</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Led by</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Jason Glade, President</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Model</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Full Service Automation</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>A century of taffy, <em>stacked by hand</em>.</h2>
      <p>Jason Glade, President of Taffy Town — a Utah candy maker with a century-long taffy tradition — needed to keep up with growth and rising national-retailer demand without piling more physical strain on his team. Hand-stacking heavy cases at the end of the bulk line was both the bottleneck and the injury risk.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Century-long taffy-making tradition</li>
        <li>Growth and rising national-retailer demand</li>
        <li>Hand-stacking heavy cases straining the team</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/taffy-town-2.jpg" alt="Taffy Town palletizing cell stacking cases" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Bulk line · automated</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic Full Service palletizing cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Low risk · high upside</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Low risk, <em>high upside</em>.</h2>
      <p>Taffy Town chose Formic's Full Service Automation — no capital to get in, nothing to program or maintain in-house — to test palletizing at low risk. Installation took only a few days after scoping, design reviews, and a 3D layout simulation. The designated palletizer was relocated to more valuable work, and when a non-Formic labeler and case taper caused a hiccup, Formic's support team diagnosed and reprogrammed it.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Full Service: no capital, nothing to maintain in-house</li>
        <li>Installed in days after a 3D layout simulation</li>
        <li>24/7 support fixed even a non-Formic device</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"We don't have to set up the system, we don't have to program it, and we don't have to maintain it. It allows us to see if palletizing automation is a good fit for us: low risk, high upside."</blockquote>
      <cite>Jason Glade · President, Taffy Town</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">5.5 million pounds. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">And counting.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">5.5M</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Lbs of taffy handled</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">279k+</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Cases stacked</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">~4,300</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Pallets built</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Scale from <em>hand to automated</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
